data.description: This cozy starter home, is a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem that offers comfortable living in a convenient location. The property offers refrigerated air, ensuring you'll stay comfortable year-round. What truly makes this property shine is its prime location. Situated in a pleasant neighborhood near shopping centers, it provides you with convenience and accessibility to essential amenities. The quiet street adds to the overall appeal, creating a tranquil and safe environment for you and your loved ones. All kitchen appliances currently present in the home will be included in the sale, ensuring that you have everything you need to start enjoying your new home right away.
